# ONLINE LEARNING PLATFORM (Coursera/Udemy) - Requirement Clarification & Discussion
## Amazon SDE2 LLD Interview Prep

---

## 🎯 Problem Statement
Design an **Online Learning Platform** (like Udemy, Coursera, Skillshare) where instructors create courses and students enroll, watch content, take quizzes, and earn certificates.

