## 🎬 Core Use Cases

### Use Case 1: Instructor Creates Course
1. Instructor logs in
2. Creates new course (title, description, price)
3. Adds modules to course
4. Adds lessons to each module
5. Adds content (video/text/quiz) to each lesson
6. Publishes course

### Use Case 2: Student Enrolls & Learns
1. Student browses courses
2. Selects a course
3. If free → Enroll directly
4. If paid → Pay → Enroll
5. Views modules and lessons
6. Watches videos, reads text
7. Takes quizzes

### Use Case 3: Student Completes Course
1. Student completes all lessons
2. Student passes all quizzes (≥70%)
3. System marks course as complete
4. Certificate is generated
5. Student can download/view certificate

### Use Case 4: Student Fails Quiz
1. Student takes quiz
2. Score < 70%
3. System shows "Failed, try again"
4. Student can retake immediately
5. Best score is stored

