## 💡 Design Patterns to Consider

| Pattern | Where | Why |
|---------|-------|-----|
| **Composite** | Course → Module → Lesson hierarchy | Tree structure |
| **Strategy** | Content types (Video, Text, Quiz) | Different content behaviors |
| **Observer** | Progress tracking | Notify when lesson complete |
| **Factory** | Content creation | Create different content types |
| **Template Method** | Quiz scoring | Same scoring algorithm, different quiz types |

