## ⚠️ Common Interview Mistakes

| Mistake | Why It's Wrong | Correct Approach |
|---------|----------------|------------------|
| No Content hierarchy | All content types mixed | Use Strategy or inheritance |
| Progress on Course | Doesn't work for multiple students | Progress on Enrollment |
| No quiz retry | Real platforms allow retries | Track best score |
| Certificate always generated | Should only be on completion | Check completion first |

